up in the front row who's got a G5 and a MacBook.

00:48:01.880 --> 00:48:02.940
He's managing it as well.

00:48:02.940 --> 00:48:10.110
Unfortunately we've got a lot of different management
products that apply to all of the different scenarios.

00:48:10.110 --> 00:48:13.760
We've got Apple Remote Desktop, which
we're going to talk about briefly.

00:48:13.760 --> 00:48:18.620
We have the system imaging tool, NetBoot,
