all of these applications?

01:02:20.980 --> 01:02:24.500
The common thread is that it's
between me and it's between you.

01:02:24.500 --> 01:02:26.550
I send you mail, you mail it back to me.

01:02:26.550 --> 01:02:29.090
I have an iChat with you, you chat with me.

01:02:29.090 --> 01:02:31.700
This information's great, but it's between you and I.

01:02:31.699 --> 01:02:33.829
It's sitting on my hard drive and
it's sitting on your hard drive.

01:02:33.829 --> 01:02:38.279
